                <h1 class="hero-title">Wachemo’s Trading Hub Awaits You</h1>
                <p class="hero-text">Imagine a place where Wachemo students and staff come together to trade. <br />
                    That’s
                    us—a
                    marketplace tailored
                    for our
                    university family. Sell your extra stuff, from books to bikes, or pick up what you need without
                    leaving
                    campus. It’s
                    safe, local, and built with you in mind. Join today and connect with your community like never
                    before!
                </P>
